Modifications made to make CasaOS work with non-systemd init systems:
- Init scripts and service definitions for multiple init systems
- Debian package structure (.deb packages)
- Universal tarball packages (.tar.gz)
- Service startup order modifications to prevent crashes
- Output redirection to /dev/null for SSD longevity
- Installation scripts for automatic OS detection and deployment
- Comprehensive documentation for each init system
- Interactive storage configuration tool to avoid flash wear

All CasaOS binaries and web UI components are unmodified from official
IceWhaleTech releases and remain under Apache License 2.0.

For the original CasaOS project, see:
https://github.com/IceWhaleTech/CasaOS
